caption: Come join us at the UTSU Clubs Fair on Friday, August 30 from 1-4PM! We will be located at the Campus Front, Section E, Table 26 where we will be handing out snacks. Feel free to chat to our executive team members at our booth for information about our organization and volunteer recruitment!! 🎶 🎶

🎶 MusicBox UofT Volunteer Music Teacher applications for the 2024-2025 year are open! 🎶

Interested in bringing the gift of music to socially and economically marginalized children? MusicBox UofT is looking for volunteers to join our team! 

🔗Apply now: bit.ly/musicbox-vol-2024 (link in bio!)
📆 Application Deadline: Sunday, September 29th, 2024 @ 11:59PM

Volunteers will receive training in delivering music programming, leadership, lesson planning, and will be eligible for CCR certification!

🌟Open to all undergraduate and graduate students at the University of Toronto St. George and Scarborough campuses.🌟

📥 Have any questions? Feel free to DM or email us at musicbox.toronto@gmail.com. We can’t wait to make music with you!
